Process a list of msrawfileRecords

scanBatchDbas.Rd

Process a list of msrawfileRecords

Usage

scanBatchDbas(records, compsToProcess = NULL, showProgress = FALSE)

Arguments

records

list of msrawfileRecords

compsToProcess

Character vector of compounds names (Default is all compounds in the spectral library)

showProgress

logical. Show progress bar (for interacte use, default false)

Value

a dbasResult object (list of 7 tables) including peakList, reintegrationResults etc.

Examples

if (FALSE) { # \dontrun{
dbComm <- getDbComm()
recs <- getTableAsRecords(
  dbComm, 
  "ntsp25.1_msrawfiles", 
  searchBlock = list(query = list(regexp = list(filename = "Des_19_.._pos.mzXML"))),
  newMsrawfilesRecord
)
recsBlanks <- getTableAsRecords(
  dbComm, 
  "ntsp25.1_msrawfiles", 
  searchBlock = list(query = list(regexp = list(path = ".*mud_pos/BW.*"))), 
  newMsrawfilesRecord
)
res <- scanBatchDbas(c(recs, recsBlanks), "Methyltriphenylphosphonium")
} # }
